## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the inherent biases in historical accounts. Additionally, while the sources provide a comprehensive overview, the complexity of international compliance and enforcement mechanisms may not be fully captured. Further research could explore the evolving nature of chemical and biological threats in the context of modern technological advancements.

